# 📝 Notes for Your Notebook

## Day 61 – Interactive Dashboard

### Topics Learned

* Navigation between multiple screens
* Reusing widgets with parameters
* `Navigator.push()`
* `Navigator.pushReplacement()`
* Creating placeholder screens

### Key Lesson

> **A dashboard is the central hub of an app. Instead of putting all features on one page, each dashboard card opens its own dedicated screen. This keeps the app organized and easier to expand.**

